title: B. toys – Stuffed Animal Dog – Super Soft & Cuddly Plush Puppy Toy – Cream & Brown – 12” – Washable – Baby, Toddler, Kid – Happy Hues – Cupcake Pup
features: Cuddle Buddy: A stuffed animal toy often becomes a baby’s best friend – which is why we at B. toys crafted the friendliest of puppies! Cupcake Pup has an extra soft cream & brown coat, patterned ears, rosy cheeks, and colorful paws. Love is a four-legged word, after all!

Soft & Squishy: Irresistibly soft, this stuffed animal dog is always up for snuggles and cuddles. Play with Cupcake Pup at home, take her on your outdoor adventures, hold her tight during story time, or make the crib cozy for bedtime.
Size: Cupcake Pup is 12 inches long – a perfect size for endless hugs!
Easy Care: This soft stuffed animal dog is machine-washable, just like your little one’s clothes!
Age: This plush dog is great for babies and big kids alike, because no one is too old for a cuddle.
description: There’s no such thing as too many cuddles with the Happy Hues Cupcake Pup from B. toys! This super soft stuffed animal toy is a plush puppy dog that comes with a few modern touches. Silky and squishy, Cupcake Pup has a cream-colored coat with brown spots, pink confetti print ears, and dark brown paws. This huggable puppy is great for playtime, bedtime, and anything-you-want time – from birth and beyond. Your little one can safely spend hours snuggling this sweet fluffy friend because she’s made with high-quality materials that are PVC-safe and phtalate-free. Not to mention that Cupcake Pup is easy to care for – she’s machine-washable! This stuffed animal dog is also made with durability in mind, because we at B. craft timeless toys that are meant to fill years and generations with love.
